  "texts": [
    "Now, based on our evaluation setup we aim to answer the following research question:Can ChatGPT support software verifiers with valid and useful loop invariants?",
    "Experimental setup.",
    "For generating loop invariants, we employ the ChatGPT (GPT-3.5) snapshot from June 2023.",
    "The model is queried via the OpenAI API 4.",
    "During our evaluation, we set the sampling temperaturefoot_4 of ChatGPT to 0.2 and sample up to k (k = 5) completions per task."
  ]
